---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/base-layout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
	pageTags={["home", "homepage"]}
	title="Mary Gold Studio | Founder-led Growth Messaging"
>
	<section class="hero">
		<div>
			<p class="kicker">Entrepreneur profile</p>
			<h1>Helping solo founders sound sharp before they scale.</h1>
			<p>
				I am Mary Gold, a strategist and product marketer who turns scattered
				offers into clear, high-conversion positioning systems. I work with
				founders who need a better website story, sharper discovery calls, and a
				lead flow that does not depend on manual follow-up.
			</p>
			<p>
				My clients are typically bootstrapped B2B founders, consultants, or
				service businesses with a strong product but weak sales messaging. The
				first thing we fix is clarity: what you sell, who it is for, and why it
				matters right now.
			</p>
			<div class="stats">
				<div class="stat">
					<strong>12 years</strong>
					<span>launch strategy</span>
				</div>
				<div class="stat">
					<strong>40+</strong>
					<span>founder teams advised</span>
				</div>
				<div class="stat">
					<strong>B2B focus</strong>
					<span>service and SaaS</span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="panel">
			<p class="kicker">Ideal client</p>
			<h2>Founder with traction, but messy qualification.</h2>
			<p>
				If your pipeline is full of vague enquiries, low-fit leads, or demo
				requests with no context, I help you replace generic contact forms with
				a guided conversation that qualifies, routes, and books.
			</p>
			<div class="widget-callout">
				<div></div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>
